.intro: A wrapper for the system ptrace header file.

This is necessary because some systems have dodgy ptrace prototypes or
don't have a prototype at all.  For example, under SunOS 4.1.X, the
ptrace prototype is given as :-

  int ptrace(int cmd, int pid, char *addr, int data);


